  "title": "Intermediary/Channel FI Junior Sales",
  "description": "<p>Our client is a large fund house with AUM of more than a billion. They are looking to hire a self-motivated and solutions-driven junior institutional fund sales executive to join their International Business Department in selling UCITs funds to fund platforms, brokers and distributors. They have a full operations team based in Singapore.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Envisaging new opportunities/product structuring/market intelligence</li>\n  <li>Relationship building with Family Offices and Wealth outfits in the Singapore region</li>\n  <li>Asset Raising in India Dedicated UCITS Funds management by the business unit</li>\n  <li>Working in conjunction with the business unit Singapore Sales Team based out of Singapore and India</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Behavioral Competencies:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Client facing, ability to coordinate with various teams</li>\n  <li>Passion to do Sales and raise Assets</li>\n  <li>Self-motivated</li>\n  <li>Ability to work independently</li>\n  <li>Analytical Skills</li>\n  <li>Strong Aptitude</li>\n  <li>Eye for detail</li>\n  <li>Detail Oriented</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Role Specific Competencies:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>MS Office (Excel, PowerPoint and Word)</li>\n  <li>Sales</li>\n  <li>Public speaking</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication skills (Verbal &amp; Written)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Position Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Has 1-2 years of experience in institutional/financial institutions sales in the asset management industry</li>\n  <li>Has 1-3 years of relevant experience in Sales/product</li>\n  <li>MBA degree holder</li>\n  <li>Internship or Management trainee experience in Mutual Fund Sales</li>\n  <li>Singapore licensed individual for Sales</li>\n  <li>Has primary understanding of the capital markets or mutual fund background</li>\n</ul>",
