    "description": "<p>\r\n\tKimberley Consulting is a leading boutique Executive Search based in Asia, specialising in human capital within specific industries including Banking and Finance, Consumer markets, FMCG, Energy and Technology, among others. </p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t </p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tWith a strong network in 11 countries in the region including Singapore, China, Japan and Korea to name a few, our global network built up over 10 years in the business has enabled us to further locate talent from different parts of the world, ensuring that the candidates we source for our clients are the best to be found. </p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t </p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tAdditionally, Kimberley Consulting also offers company incorporation and related consulting services to foreign-based companies looking to move into Singapore. We assist in all processes involved in the setting up of offices in Singapore, including office re-locations, managing manpower staffing needs and other services as required. </p>\r\n",
